{"text_id":211250,"tokens":["\u0093","In"," this"," work",","," we"," propose"," a"," new"," smooth"," hybrid"," inflation"," model"," that"," addresses"," the"," issues"," of"," initial"," conditions"," and"," Grace","ful"," Exit"," present"," in"," traditional"," hybrid"," inflation"," models","."," Our"," approach"," incorporates"," a"," Coleman","-","Wein","berg"," potential"," with"," a"," non","-","minimal"," kinetic"," term",","," leading"," to"," a"," successful"," inflationary"," period"," followed"," by"," a"," graceful"," exit"," to"," a"," radiation","-","dominated"," universe","."," We"," demonstrate"," that"," the"," addition"," of"," a"," new"," scalar"," field",","," which"," we"," call"," the"," ","\u0093","smooth","''"," field",","," enables"," a"," smooth"," transition"," between"," the"," inflationary"," and"," radiation"," eras",".","\n\n","To"," derive"," our"," model",","," we"," first"," assume"," a"," super","gravity"," framework"," with"," two"," chiral"," super","fields",","," one"," driving"," inflation"," and"," the"," other"," acting"," as"," the"," ","\u0093","smooth","''"," field","."," We"," then"," consider"," a"," specific"," form"," of"," the"," super","potential",","," ensuring"," the"," flat","ness"," of"," the"," inflationary"," potential"," and"," a"," waterfall"," mechanism"," for"," the"," Grace","ful"," Exit","."," Next",","," we"," derive"," the"," equations"," of"," motion"," and"," solve"," them"," numerically",","," displaying"," the"," dynamics"," of"," the"," inflationary"," and"," radiation"," eras",".","\n\n","The"," results"," reveal"," that"," our"," new"," smooth"," hybrid"," inflation"," model"," successfully"," satisfies"," the"," cosmological"," observables",","," including"," the"," scalar"," spectral"," index",","," the"," tensor","-","to","-","scalar"," ratio",","," and"," the"," running"," of"," the"," spectral"," index","."," Moreover",","," the"," inclusion"," of"," the"," non","-","minimal"," kinetic"," term"," allows"," for"," the"," possibility"," of"," a"," hill","top"," or"," saddle"," point"," inflation",","," offering"," a"," new"," perspective"," on"," the"," dynamics"," of"," inflation",".","\n\n","Overall",","," our"," proposed"," smooth"," hybrid"," inflation"," model"," aims"," to"," solve"," the"," initial"," conditions"," and"," Grace","ful"," Exit"," issues"," present"," in"," traditional"," models"," while"," maintaining"," consistency"," with"," cosmological"," data","."," This"," advances"," our"," understanding"," of"," the"," early"," universe"," and"," p","aves"," the"," way"," for"," further"," explorations"," of"," inflationary"," scenarios"," in"," the"," context"," of"," high","-","energy"," physics",".","\u0094"],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}